subject: Customize Parameterized class report?
msgSnippet: Hello everybody, Is it possible to customize the output reports from tests running with @RunWith(value=Parameterized.class) For example instead of [0], [1]
messageBody:
Hello everybody,

Is it possible to customize the output reports from tests running with
@RunWith(value=Parameterized.class)

For example instead of [0], [1] ,[2], [3].
Getting the names of the input parameters.


Thanks.

El Moumen
